### libkanberra 0.31

  * initial commit: libcanberra 0.30 fork
  * ci: enable Github Actions
  * Play login sound in Unity too if it's enabled (it's disabled by default in Ubuntu)
  * gtk: Don't assume all GdkDisplays are GdkX11Displays
  * Fix FTBFS with binutils-gold
  * port from GTK to CTK
  * drop vala code
  * remove Makefile.in
  * gtkdoc,tmpl: remove blank lines at EOF
  * remove trailing whitespaces
  * rename canberra -> kanberra
  * rename ca_ -> ka_
  * kanberra-ctk-play: avoid deprecated 'g_type_init'
  * kanberra-ctk: avoid deprecated 'cdk_screen_get_number'
  * kanberra-ctk: WidthOfScreen and HeightOfScreen implementation
  * kanberra-ctk-module: avoid deprecated 'cdk_error_trap_push' and 'cdk_error_trap_pop_ignored'
  * update README
  * remove 'configure' file
